author: Catharine Tunney
title: Ottawa 'likely did not have enough' protective gear stockpiled: Hajdu
description: Federal Health Minister Patty Hajdu said today Ottawa "likely did not have enough" personal protective gear in the national stockpile heading into the COVID-19 pandemic.
content:
Federal Health Minister Patty Hajdu said today Ottawa "likely did not have enough" personal protective gear in the national stockpile heading into the COVID-19 pandemic.
